Class Description
Actor
The abstract class Actor defines common methods of all Actors which are its subclasses.

The class BackgroundImage is a background for the Level classes.

The class Crocodile is a Rideable that can be ridden by Player when intersected.

The class Digit is a changeable Actor that shows a number between 0-9.
